            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-6" data-ani="slideinright">
          <div style="padding-left: 20px;">
            <h2 style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 700; color: #113D48; margin-bottom: 16px;">Group and VIP Transfers</h2>
            <p style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.8; color: #4a5568; margin-bottom: 16px;">
              For larger groups, corporate events and VIP guests, we connect you with premium minibus and coach services. Luxury leather interiors, air conditioning and professional drivers who ensure your group travels in comfort.
            </p>
            <p style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.8; color: #4a5568;">
              Whether it is an airport pick-up for a conference group, a wedding party transfer or daily transportation for a corporate incentive trip — the right vehicle and the right service make all the difference.
            </p>
            <a href="https://www.rhodestransfer24.com/" target="_blank" style="display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; margin-top: 16px; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 600; color: #1CA8CB; text-decoration: none;">Book at RhodesTransfer24.com <i class="fas fa-arrow-right" style="font-size: 0.75rem;"></i></a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 6. Transfer Info -->
  <section style="padding: 40px 0 60px; background: #f8fafb;">
    <div class="container">
      <div style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto;">
        <div class="tr-flow" data-ani="fadein">
          <h2 style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1.35rem; font-weight: 700; color: #113D48; margin: 0 0 16px;">Transportation in Rhodes</h2>
          <p>When visiting Rhodes, transportation is an important part of your trip, especially when you need to move between the airport, your hotel, the port or the marina where your boat departs. We work with reliable local transfer companies that provide professional transportation services around the island.</p>

          <h2 style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1.35rem; font-weight: 700; color: #113D48; margin: 32px 0 16px;">Transfer Services Available</h2>
          <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 6px 24px; margin-bottom: 20px;" class="tr-list-grid">
            <p style="margin: 0; padding: 6px 0;"><i class="fas fa-check" style="color: #1CA8CB; margin-right: 8px; font-size: 0.8rem;"></i>Airport transfers</p>
            <p style="margin: 0; padding: 6px 0;"><i class="fas fa-check" style="color: #1CA8CB; margin-right: 8px; font-size: 0.8rem;"></i>Hotel transfers</p>
            <p style="margin: 0; padding: 6px 0;"><i class="fas fa-check" style="color: #1CA8CB; margin-right: 8px; font-size: 0.8rem;"></i>Port transfers</p>
            <p style="margin: 0; padding: 6px 0;"><i class="fas fa-check" style="color: #1CA8CB; margin-right: 8px; font-size: 0.8rem;"></i>Marina transfers</p>
            <p style="margin: 0; padding: 6px 0;"><i class="fas fa-check" style="color: #1CA8CB; margin-right: 8px; font-size: 0.8rem;"></i>Weddings and events</p>
            <p style="margin: 0; padding: 6px 0;"><i class="fas fa-check" style="color: #1CA8CB; margin-right: 8px; font-size: 0.8rem;"></i>Corporate groups</p>
            <p style="margin: 0; padding: 6px 0;"><i class="fas fa-check" style="color: #1CA8CB; margin-right: 8px; font-size: 0.8rem;"></i>VIP transfers</p>
            <p style="margin: 0; padding: 6px 0;"><i class="fas fa-check" style="color: #1CA8CB; margin-right: 8px; font-size: 0.8rem;"></i>Private island tours</p>
          </div>

          <h2 style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1.35rem; font-weight: 700; color: #113D48; margin: 32px 0 16px;">Transfers to Boat Departure Points</h2>
          <p>If you are joining a boat tour, a sailing trip, a yacht charter or any sea activity, you may need transportation to the marina or harbour. Transfers can be arranged to Mandraki Harbour, Rhodes New Marina, Faliraki, Kolymbia, Lindos and other locations. We always recommend arranging your transfer in advance so your day can start smoothly.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 4. Recommended Partner -->
  <section style="padding: 60px 0;">
    <div class="container">
      <div style="max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: center;">
        <h2 style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1.35rem; font-weight: 700; color: #113D48; margin-bottom: 16px;" data-ani="slideinup">Recommended Transfer Company</h2>
        <p style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; color: #6b7c85; margin-bottom: 28px;" data-ani="fadein" data-ani-delay="0.1">
          One of the transfer companies we recommend in Rhodes is <strong style="color: #113D48;">RhodesTransfer24</strong>, a professional transfer company offering airport transfers, hotel transfers, group transportation and private transfers across the island with modern vehicles and professional drivers.
        </p>
        <a href="https://www.rhodostransfer24.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="th-btn style3 th-icon" data-ani="slideinup" data-ani-delay="0.2">Visit RhodesTransfer24.com <i class="fas fa-external-link-alt" style="margin-left: 6px; font-size: 0.8rem;"></i></a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 5. Contact -->
  <section style="padding: 80px 0; background: #113D48;">
    <div class="container">
      <div style="max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: center;">
        <h2 style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 3vw, 2rem); font-weight: 700; color: #fff; margin-bottom: 20px;" data-ani="slideinup">Need Help Arranging a Transfer?</h2>
        <p style="font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); margin-bottom: 36px;" data-ani="fadein" data-ani-delay="0.1">
          If you need transportation during your stay in Rhodes — from the airport, your hotel, the port or the marina — book directly with our recommended partner <a href="https://www.rhodestransfer24.com/" target="_blank" style="color: #fff; text-decoration: underline;">RhodesTransfer24.com</a>.
        </p>
        <div style="display: flex; gap: 16px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap;" data-ani="slideinup" data-ani-delay="0.2">
          <a href="https://www.rhodestransfer24.com/" target="_blank" style="display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; padding: 14px 28px; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 600; color: #113D48; background: #fff; border-radius: 8px; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.3s ease;"><i class="fas fa-car"></i> Book Your Transfer</a>
          <a href="/contact" class="th-btn style3 th-icon">Contact Us</a>
          <a href="https://wa.me/302241012345" style="display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; padding: 14px 28px; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; font-size: 0.85rem; font-weight: 600; color: #fff; border: 1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3); border-radius: 8px; text-decoration: none; transition: all 0.3s ease;"><i class="fab fa-whatsapp"></i> WhatsApp</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <FooterFour />
</BaseLayout>

<script>
  document.getElementById('header-one')?.classList.add('header-transparent');

  // Image carousel
  function initTransferCarousel() {
    const images = document.querySelectorAll('.tr-carousel-track img');
    const dots = document.querySelectorAll('.tr-dot');
    if (!images.length) return;
    let current = 0;
    let interval: ReturnType<typeof setInterval>;

    function show(index: number) {
      images.forEach((img, i) => {
        (img as HTMLElement).style.opacity = i === index ? '1' : '0';
        (img as HTMLElement).style.transition = 'opacity 0.6s ease';
      });
      dots.forEach((dot, i) => {
        (dot as HTMLElement).style.opacity = i === index ? '1' : '0.4';
      });
      current = index;
    }

    function next() {
      show((current + 1) % images.length);
    }

    dots.forEach((dot, i) => {
      dot.addEventListener('click', () => {
        show(i);
        clearInterval(interval);
        interval = setInterval(next, 4000);
      });
    });

    interval = setInterval(next, 4000);
  }

  function initTransferCarousel2() {
    const images = document.querySelectorAll('.tr-carousel2-track img');
    const dots = document.querySelectorAll('.tr-dot2');
    if (!images.length) return;
    let current = 0;
    let interval: ReturnType<typeof setInterval>;

    function show(index: number) {
      images.forEach((img, i) => {
        (img as HTMLElement).style.opacity = i === index ? '1' : '0';
        (img as HTMLElement).style.transition = 'opacity 0.6s ease';
      });
      dots.forEach((dot, i) => {
        (dot as HTMLElement).style.opacity = i === index ? '1' : '0.4';
      });
      current = index;
    }

    function next() {
      show((current + 1) % images.length);
    }

    dots.forEach((dot, i) => {
      dot.addEventListener('click', () => {
        show(i);
        clearInterval(interval);
        interval = setInterval(next, 4500);
      });
    });

    interval = setInterval(next, 4500);
  }

  function initTransferCarousel3() {
    const images = document.querySelectorAll('.tr-carousel3-track img');
    const dots = document.querySelectorAll('.tr-dot3');
    if (!images.length) return;
    let current = 0;
    let interval: ReturnType<typeof setInterval>;

    function show(index: number) {
      images.forEach((img, i) => {
        (img as HTMLElement).style.opacity = i === index ? '1' : '0';
        (img as HTMLElement).style.transition = 'opacity 0.6s ease';
      });
      dots.forEach((dot, i) => {
        (dot as HTMLElement).style.opacity = i === index ? '1' : '0.4';
      });
      current = index;
    }

    function next() {
      show((current + 1) % images.length);
    }

    dots.forEach((dot, i) => {
      dot.addEventListener('click', () => {
        show(i);
        clearInterval(interval);
        interval = setInterval(next, 4000);
      });
    });

    interval = setInterval(next, 4000);
  }

  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => { initTransferCarousel(); initTransferCarousel2(); initTransferCarousel3(); });
  document.addEventListener('astro:page-load', () => { initTransferCarousel(); initTransferCarousel2(); initTransferCarousel3(); });
</script>

<style>
  .tr-flow {
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.02rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: #4a5568;
  }

  .tr-flow p {
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 991px) {
    .tr-intro-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr !important;
      gap: 0 !important;
    }
    .tr-list-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr !important;
    }
  }
</style>
